******
[5] USA (Michigan): monitoring 14 individuals for Ebola infection
Date: Thu 24 Dec 2014
Source: Michigan Emerging Diseases [edited]
http://www.michigan.gov/emergingdiseases/0,4579,7-186-69879---,00.html


Monitoring individuals for Ebola infection
------------------------------------------
There are currently 14 individuals being actively monitored (including one who is being monitored more carefully) in Michigan (52 have cleared [the 21-day quarantine period, which] includes twice daily measurement of temperature and monitoring of symptoms) [see guidance document for Michigan: http://www.michigan.gov/documents/emergingdiseases/Michigan_EBOLA_Guidance_464829_7.pdf]. The Michigan Department of Community Health and the State network of local public health agencies are currently supporting the monitoring of individuals with a travel history that includes a return to the state from Ebola affected areas.

